SafeArk products help you control home appliance nice and easy. You can simply ask Alexa to show the online video of SafeArk devices. After connecting Alexa to your SafeArk products in a few simple steps:
1. Download our “SafeArk” app in app market then register an account (or log in directly if you already have an account);
2. Configure our devices in “SafeArk” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
3. Enable “SafeArk” skill on Alexa app, you'll be navigated to the login page, follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
4. Tell Echo "Alexa, discover my devices". Wait for Echo to say “Search complete”;
5. Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
Alexa, show me the camera.
Alexa, show me the backyard camera.
